description: This Web site discusses and provides downloadable data on state and program type, number of children ever enrolled, and the percentage of growth compared to the previous FY. It also provides links to data downloads about the Childrens Health Insurance Program Reauthorization Act (CHIPRA) Connecting Kids to Coverage Challenge, CHIP Reports and Evaluations, and CHIP state program information.
keyword: Publically Available Data File - for download
title: Childrens Health Insurance Program (CHIP)
